    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors assessed or flagged. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors not assessed and flagged as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Despite the gap between achieved and required credibility levels across all assessed factors, the package is accepted as a complete credibility assessment submission documenting the known deficiencies. The mesh independence study was declared as a completed VerificationActivity; however, the evidence artifacts documenting GCI computation results have not been linked to this activity, representing a consistency gap that must be resolved prior to regulatory submission.",
